00:31:14,359 --> 00:31:14,880
Darn it.

575
00:31:15,359 --> 00:31:16,319
We've got a tail.

576
00:31:17,119 --> 00:31:18,039
I'll go distract them.

577
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:28,480
Spread out and sit.

578
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,599
Monkey head mushroom.

579
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,480
Monkey head mushroom.

580
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:43,640
Cigarettes.

581
00:31:59,759 --> 00:32:00,960
Hello sir, what would you like to drink?

582
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,160
A cup of tea, please.

583
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:03,559
Alright, coming right up.

584
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:57,960
Please enjoy your meal, sir.

585
00:33:14,319 --> 00:33:14,920
Don't move.

586
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,279
Let's go.

587
00:33:59,599 --> 00:34:00,559
Let's talk somewhere else.

588
00:34:07,480 --> 00:34:08,280
Li Zhenghao

589
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:40,800
Hurry, go this way!

590
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:42,599
Yunhu, go!

591
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:43,800
Hurry!

592
00:34:50,599 --> 00:34:51,039
Go!

593
00:34:58,679 --> 00:34:59,599
Quick, this way!

594
00:35:07,039 --> 00:35:07,559
What’s wrong?

595
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:10,760
I’m getting old.

596
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:11,920
I can’t outrun bullets anymore.

597
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:12,800
Platoon leader.

598
00:35:13,039 --> 00:35:14,239
Fu Qing and I will draw the enemy away.

599
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:14,920
You go first.

600
00:35:15,199 --> 00:35:15,639
Okay.

601
00:35:15,719 --> 00:35:16,239
Be careful.

602
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:18,559
Come on, get up.

603
00:35:19,039 --> 00:35:19,599
Hurry!

604
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:20,440
Get up!

605
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:21,760
Go!

606
00:35:33,239 --> 00:35:35,159
Block off this road!

607
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:35,760
Yes!

608
00:35:49,599 --> 00:35:50,440
After them!

609
00:35:51,639 --> 00:35:52,320
Hurry up!

610
00:36:11,639 --> 00:36:12,159
That way!

611
00:36:12,199 --> 00:36:12,599
That way!

612
00:36:14,679 --> 00:36:15,519
Papers.

613
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:53,400
Here.

614
00:36:58,880 --> 00:36:59,639
Any suspicious people found?

615
00:36:59,639 --> 00:37:00,000
No.

616
00:37:00,159 --> 00:37:00,679
Keep searching.

617
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:01,119
Yes.

618
00:37:04,039 --> 00:37:04,599
Come here, come here.

619
00:37:19,679 --> 00:37:21,239
Damn, it's a dead end.

620
00:37:25,719 --> 00:37:26,199
This way.

621
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,159
Come.

622
00:37:35,079 --> 00:37:35,440
Come.

623
00:38:44,679 --> 00:38:45,039
Come.

624
00:38:50,239 --> 00:38:50,920
Go, quickly!

625
00:38:51,440 --> 00:38:52,239
I can't leave.

626
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:53,800
We've never abandoned

627
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:54,719
any comrade.

628
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:56,199
Go!

629
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:09,239
I wish I could meet more comrades.

630
00:39:11,639 --> 00:39:13,079
Hurry, go!

631
00:39:16,239 --> 00:39:16,679
Shoot!

632
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:27,360
Look at that.

633
00:40:28,079 --> 00:40:28,679
See?

634
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,280
It’s still bleeding, look.

635
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,159
Who is that?

636
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:35,320
A Japanese officer just said,

637
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:36,639
it’s a Communist.

638
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:38,360
How awful!

639
00:40:39,119 --> 00:40:40,559
The Japanese are so cruel.

640
00:40:42,239 --> 00:40:43,360
That’s outrageous.

641
00:40:44,239 --> 00:40:45,159
Look over there.

642
00:40:45,239 --> 00:40:45,880
There’s still blood.

643
00:42:05,119 --> 00:42:11,639
You think of me in the dead of night,

644
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:15,840
and play the yaoqin for me.

645
00:42:19,679 --> 00:42:25,639
I think of you at midnight,

646
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:29,239
and go to the garden to offer incense.

647
00:42:32,559 --> 00:42:38,679
You think of me in the study,

648
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:43,960
unable to focus on the classics.

649
00:42:47,679 --> 00:42:54,480
I think of you in the embroidery room,

650
00:42:54,599 --> 00:42:59,599
too distracted to embroider mandarin ducks.
